Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to change the subject, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, do you all have\Nplans for winter vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since the Phoenix Festa\Nwas such a learning experience for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd take this\Nopportunity to re-train myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to go through\Nmy usual regimen, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're finally getting some time off,\NI thought I'd take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really? A quiet New Year's holiday...\NThat sounds pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So sleep through New Year's\Nwith me, Aya—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there's something\NI'd like to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.07,0:00:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, everybody!\NI've come to pick you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:07.06,Loc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KINGDOM OF LIESELTANIA, CAPITAL: STOREL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Princess Julis! Welcome home!\N- Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.75,0:01:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How'd we end up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:05.93,ArcName,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lieseltania
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Julis! Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, Julis and Claudia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like a word with my brother\Nif you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know you helped Flora\Nduring the Phoenix Festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I invited you all here\Nso that I could thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm happy\Nyou've accepted my invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Julis's older brother, Jolbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say\Nthat I'm the king of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this is my wife, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's very nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,King?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one ever told me anything\Nabout a victory parade!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I told you,\Nyou would've hated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I would've!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Putting me through it is one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but what were you thinking,\Ndragging Ayato into it, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you ever heard\Nof consulting people in advance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right. I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the people are intrigued,\Nnot just by you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but by your tag partner,\NAmagiri, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he's the partner\Ntheir princess hand-picked herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it only the citizens\Nwho are intrigued by him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, you're as perceptive as always,\Naren't you, my dear Ms. Enfield?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we could\Ndiscuss that another time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have so many other things\NI want to talk to you and Amagiri about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure. Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a banquet planned\Nfor tomorrow night to welcome you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I hope you'll all attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! In the springtime, there are flowers\Neverywhere, so it's even prettier!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had you come because I wanted you\Nto see my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry it turned into such a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is really something.\NThese buildings are so imposing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this garden and villa were built\Nduring the time of the Holy Roman Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Later, it gained its independence\Nas the Kingdom of Lieseltania,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,only to be wiped out\Nin the German revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But then after the Invertia,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,an extremely rare Grade A\NBeltis meteorite of the highest caliber
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,was discovered in one of Lieseltania's\Nformer territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the Integrated Enterprise Foundation\Nbegan fighting over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But a serious military confrontation\Nwould've been too risky for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So they signed an agreement\Nto distribute the profits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:06:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then they thought they might\Nas well create a playground for themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and resurrected the country\Nthat existed there before... Lieseltania.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, a puppet state?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To put it bluntly, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why my country is under their\Ntight control in every way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we do receive some\Nfinancial benefits, but as for the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So many people are suffering\Nfrom the disparity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to change this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I cannot concede no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Of course, I'm entirely aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Mr. Amagiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Flora?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's almost time for dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but Lady Sasamiya isn't in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya's directionally-challenged,\Nso she might be lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I think I have\Na good idea where she might be,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll help you look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya, I hear that dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,always wanted to tell you I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... for what, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After I moved away,\Nyou and I kept in touch. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But then it got too painful for me,\Nand I was the one who stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is that what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because... Before, we used to\Nplay together everyday,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but after I moved,\NI could only talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And only for a really short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At first, that was\Nwhat I looked forward to,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but before I knew it,\Nit had become painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I decided... until the day came\Nwe could properly meet again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not really such a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we'd kept in touch the whole time,\Nthen when Big Sis Haru went missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I might've been able to help you, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I couldn't help,\NI could've cheered you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could've supported you, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that... that's what\Nmakes me so frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I should've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd always been by your side, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, Ayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to lean on me\Nwhen you need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This time for sure,\NI'm going to be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:08:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What I'm supposed to do right now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Julis, it's to be there for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that day ever comes,\NI'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's hungry and waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'd like to take this\Nopportunity to consult you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's about next year's Festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like all of you present to take part\Nin the Gryps Festa as my teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did invite Ayato before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His answer then was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If Julis joins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still feel the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis. How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before I answer,\Nthere's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so obsessed\Nwith the Gryps Festa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You could easily advance\Nin the Phoenix Festa or the Lindwurs Festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True, I'd be sure to advance,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it would be difficult\Nfor me to win it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that would be unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have a chance in the Gryps Festa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, as long as I have\Ndependable teammates, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go further into detail after you've\Nagreed to become my teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since it has to do with my\Nweakness, as well as this one's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Precognition has a weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No weapon is infallible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you're powerful\Neven without the Pan-Dora, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, my powers without the Pan-Dora\Nare quite pedestrian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's precisely why I need\Npowerful comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, anyone who hopes\Nto win the Gryps Festa
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will need to defeat those Lifelordes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The team of Zhao Hufeng and Cecily Wong,\Nformer Phoenix Festa runners-up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will surely compete for Jie Long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I hear that Divine Revelations'\N#1 disciple, too, will be on this team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, you mean Hagun Seikun,\Ntheir Rank #2?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I hear it's very terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We also can't underestimate\NRusalka of Queenvail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And there are sure to be other\Nformidable teams in our path.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True, it probably won't be easy\Nto win the next Gryps Festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I do believe that with you\Non my team, we have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take part as a member of your team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No reason to decline, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:12:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That really looks good\Non you, Mr. Amagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think so? I've never dressed\Nthis way before, so it makes me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Mr. Amagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not allowed\Nto carry weapons during parties,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll hold onto that for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis? I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right. Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you\Nstanding there in a daze for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's right, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At times like these, you're expected\Nto pay compliments to the ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I don't look good in this...\Nso you don't have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you all look great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:12:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That becomes you quite well, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I'd really prefer\Nthat you escorted me, Ayato,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but as Julis is the guest of honor...\NI'll have to live with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In return, please be sure\Nto pay us some attention later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I suppose I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. This is what you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bend your elbow a little. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If push comes to shove, I'll lead the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You look pretty exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought\Nthere'd be this many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to say this... but I thought\Nyour family had no money?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This country may have\Nmoney to spend on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I have none to use myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, my brother isn't like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My brother never speaks out politically,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and he has no enthusiasm for his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that he's the ideal puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.57,0:14:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the Integrated Enterprise\NFoundation treasures him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and why they ignore it\Nwhen he wants to have his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, those women\Nare my brother's lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lovers... Is he really\Nbeing that bold about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They, like Maria, were sent here\Nby the Integrated Enterprise Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't go so far as\Nto call them spies, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my sister-in-law\Nis a genuine airhead,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so in her case,\Nignorance is probably bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not like I dislike\Nmy sister-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As for Claudia,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,her father is in charge\Nof this region of the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's visited Lieseltania with her father\Nnumerous times since childhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which is why she's friendly\Nwith my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is Claudia's dad also an Integrated\NEnterprise Foundation executive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's more like her mother's\Npersonal subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He probably has no chance\Nof becoming an executive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's too human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to become an executive
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,at the Integrated Enterprise Foundation\Nis to lose your humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, for me personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,her father had a more favorable\Nimpression on me than her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, I could tell\Nthat he cared for his daughter deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get into another\Nconversation like yesterday, so you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:15:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'm going to go\Nget some air over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That dress looks divine on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right. Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You fought so magnificently\Nin the Phoenix Festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have your sword on you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin, do you have a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'm sorry! Please excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Ayato-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hard for me to talk\Nto people I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And besides...\NI'm not pretty like the senpais.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-But... A dress like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It just doesn't fit a child like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said before,\Nyou look great in that dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really grown-up and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Th-Thank you... very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right! See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask of you.\NDo you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... I'd like to link arms\Nwith you, too, Ayato-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-When you did it with Julis-senpai\Nearlier, it looked so lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know\Nif I can be a proper escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's fine! If you could just\Ndo that for me, I'd be so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Kirin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we should\Nbe this close together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, having him all to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saya! What's up\Nwith that all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to link arms with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's what you call\Na pretty girl on each arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I must say, I do like to see\Nthat kind of spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just what you'd expect of someone\Nwho made his mark in the Phoenix Festa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, are you planning to take part\Nin the next Gryps Festa, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor has it that you'll be\Njoining Ms. Enfield's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I haven't quite decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it would be in your\Nbest interests not to join her team.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Just what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't bode well\Nfor a certain someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,should you join Ms. Enfield's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My job is to find a way\Nto somehow stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so I've come to make that request.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if I refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That would be extremely unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Having to dispatch an innocent youth\Nwould pain my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so... that job shall go to this child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}38-type Lux grenade launcher...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hernekraume.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That I'd come to your aid, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin, you stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri Shinmei Style\NGrappling Skill...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Coffin Feather Drill!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri Shinmei Style...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unbreakable Thunder!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.43,0:21:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya! Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Leave it to us!\N- Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hernekraume!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- Amaryllis!\N- Kaboom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So even a chimera is no match for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.67,0:21:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to do all that\Nwithout a weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he's going to be a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would've preferred not to get\Ntoo involved on this level, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.11,0:23:32.08,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of my dance moves,\Npolished by high society?
